            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De tranquillitate populi</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
      Â¶ De tranquillitate populorum. Rubrica. 11 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>
      <ref>CAssiodorus eri li. i
      <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>.c. i.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e125">Omni
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>quippe regno desiderabilis debet
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>esse tranquillitas in qua et populi pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>ficiunt: et vtilitas gentium custoditur. Hec est
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>enim bonarum artium mater: hec mortalium
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>genus reparabili successione multiplicans fa
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>cultates protendit: mores extollit. Et tanta
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>rum rerum ignarus agnoscitur qui eam mi
        <lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>nime quesisse sentitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e146"> /
       <ref>4. e.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e148">Cogi debet vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>sit quietus qui suo vicio renuit esse paci
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>ficus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e157"> /
            <ref>22 e.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e159">Decet regalis apicis curam ge
        <lb ed="#V" n="80" break="no"/>neralitatis custodire concordiam. Ad laudem
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>regnantis trahitur si ab omnibus pax ametur</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e167">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/> /
               <ref>Libro. 2 e. 29.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e171">Regnantis est gloria subie
        <lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>ctorum ociosa tranquillitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e177"> /
            <ref>Lib. 3. e. 38</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e179">Principis opinionem longe lateque disseminat
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>subiectorum custodita securitas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e187"> /
            <ref>Li. 5. e. 39</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e189">Quies suauissima populi et dispositio tran
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>quilla regionum preconium probatur esse regnan
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>tium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-d1e199"> /
            <ref>Lib. 11. e. 9.</ref><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d34747-Qd1e201">Furoris genus est in se
        <lb ed="#V" n="89" break="no"/>culo pacato turbulento studere proposito. <!--118.xml-->
               </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
